# Winston Wolf — proof-of-life experiment (004) crontab
# Install on the VPS AFTER `ww-outreach auth` has minted a richbond.ma token.
#   1. set ENGINE_DIR + CAMPAIGN below
#   2. crontab -e  and paste the three lines (adjust paths)
#   3. confirm: crontab -l
#
# Reply detection is MANUAL (Article 15) — there is intentionally NO detect pass.
# `review` (morning approval gate) and `flag-replied` are run by the operator, not cron.

# --- edit these ---
# ENGINE_DIR=/home/djaafar/winston-wolf/engine
# CAMPAIGN=richbond-pilot
# (cron has no variables — substitute the literal paths/id into the lines below)

# nightly draft: research → grounded draft + reasoning note → review file (off-peak batches)
30 2-5 * * *  cd /home/djaafar/winston-wolf/engine && uv run ww-engine draft    --campaign richbond-pilot --batch 15  >> /home/djaafar/winston-wolf/data/logs/draft.log 2>&1

# hourly deliver: sends only inside each recipient's local Tue-Thu 10-14 window
0  *   * * *  cd /home/djaafar/winston-wolf/engine && uv run ww-engine deliver   --campaign richbond-pilot                >> /home/djaafar/winston-wolf/data/logs/deliver.log 2>&1

# evening conclude: turn review comments into dated observations for the next draft pass
0  20  * * *  cd /home/djaafar/winston-wolf/engine && uv run ww-engine conclude  --campaign richbond-pilot               >> /home/djaafar/winston-wolf/data/logs/conclude.log 2>&1
